    <Text id="2" huntingZoneId="63" prevId="0" villagerId="1604">
        <Page social="0">The federation needs veteran's greatswords. I have materials for you, if you're up for it.</Page>
    </Text>
    <Text id="3" huntingZoneId="63" prevId="2" villagerId="1604">
        <Page social="0">These will do nicely. Will you run these out to Baruch in Tulufan?&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;He's got slayers in need of weapons.</Page>
    </Text>
    <Text id="4" huntingZoneId="63" villagerId="1604">
        <Page social="0">You've got the design and kits—talk to the crafting vendors if you need additional materials.</Page>
    </Text>
    <Text id="5" huntingZoneId="66" prevId="3" villagerId="1001">
        <Page social="0">Just what we needed! Splendid work and timing!</Page>
    </Text>
